    • getTop3Items

      private void getTop3Items()
      first get every single item in items_separate_orders view put them all in a giant arraylist get the first menu item from the menu table and call the string item1 get the second menu item etc... put all the menu items in an arraylist set mostFreq item = menu.get(0) set itemCount = 0 set maxCount = 0 do a loop where you increment itemCount whenever orders(i) = menu(j) inc i every time, once at the end of the list, inc j, each time you go through the list, if maxCount is less than itemCount mostFreqItem = menu(j) maxCount = itemCount itemCount = 0
